text: Staffan Lidbeck (born 12 June 1968) is a Swedish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
